comment: Fournier (ORL) makes marginal contact with Porter (WAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
Beal (WAS) makes incidental contact with Biyombo (ORL) that does not affect his FOM.
Morris (WAS) is in the lane for more than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Fournier (ORL) makes marginal contact with Gortat (WAS) and does not extend his elbow into him.
Payton (ORL) makes contact with Wall (WAS) that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Ibaka (ORL) sets the screen on Wall (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) is firming up at the time of the contact with Beal (WAS) on the screen.
Ibaka (ORL) makes marginal contact with Wall (WAS) that does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Wall (WAS) makes marginal contact with Payton (ORL) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Beal (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players then briefly engage.
Fournier (ORL) and Thornton (WAS) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Payton (ORL) makes contact with Wall (WAS) that affects his FOM away from the play.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor is confirmed.
